Unrivaled Spear DemonShuji, a soldier who danced with death many times while on the battlefield, was
possessed by the grudges and resentment of those he had killed. He too was
eventually killed, but somehow he awoke in a younger version of himself.



He returned to a time when he was still an errand boy, inexperienced with war,
but retained his memories. Remembering Kyo Aiyo, his comrade and savior, Shuji
travelled to the ‘Tiger Pit’ Sect. However, instead of the strong and reliable
woman, he was met with a cheerful and petite girl. He recalled the tragic past
that had caused her to devote herself to the army, where in his previous life
her family had fallen apart due to false rumors.



‘This time, I will protect you.’



He vowed to repay the kindness he received in his previous life by changing her
fate. With a spear in his right hand, Shuji steps into the battlefield once
